      Capturing spectacular views along the dramatic coastline and far out to sea, it reveals a striking tri-level design with stylish contemporary interiors and premium finishes throughout.
      
      Cleverly engineered with multiple balconies allowing effortless cross-ventilation, it features generous proportions with separate family living and dining areas while at the heart of the home is a gourmet marble kitchen equipped with a suite of integrated Gaggenau gas appliances.
      
      Bi-fold doors allow a seamless flow to a tranquil north facing backyard oasis, complete with a sun bathed entertainment courtyard and a glass fenced mosaic-tiled swimming pool in lush garden surrounds.
